  "content": "\n \n \n  <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack article_content__xNUGz\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:24px\" data-customer-story=\"false\">\n   <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack article_dateAndTimeToRead__6RnTk\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:row;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:space-between;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-x-2 sm:gap-x-6\">\n     <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:row;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:6px\">\n      <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:0px;--text-weight:400\"><br></p></div></div></div>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/functions/runtimes/node-js\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Vercel Functions using Node.js</a> can now detect when a request is canceled and stop execution before completion. This includes actions like navigating away, closing a tab, or hitting stop on an AI chat to terminate compute processing early.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">This reduces unnecessary compute, token generation, and sending data the user won’t see.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">You can listen for cancellation using <code>Request.signal.aborted</code> or the <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbortSignal\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\"><code>abort</code></a> event:</p>\n   <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-code-block_wrapper__G_cQP\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:16px\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block_wrapper__t6FCO blog-code-block_codeBlock__s7CJU\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block_copyButton__uo5Yu code-block_copyFloatingButton__PsMvB\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-javascript code-block_pre___OLfy blog-code-block_maxHeight__pAjn3\"><code class=\"code-block_code__isn_V\"><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword module\">export</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function-variable function maybe-class-name\">GET</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">async</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">req</span><span class=\"token parameter operator\">:</span><span class=\"token parameter\"> Request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token arrow operator\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> abortController </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token class-name\">AbortController</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  req</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">signal</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"abort\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token arrow operator\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token console class-name\">console</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"request aborted\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    abortController</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">abort</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> res </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword control-flow\">await</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"https://my-backend-service.example.com\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    headers</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      </span><span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">Authorization</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token template-string template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token template-string string\">Bearer </span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation\">process</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation\">env</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation constant\">AUTH_TOKEN</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token template-string template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    signal</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> abortController</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">signal</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token keyword control-flow\">return</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token class-name\">Response</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token plain\">res</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    status</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> res</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">status</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    headers</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> res</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">headers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:initial;--text-weight:400;--text-align:center\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">If you're using the <a href=\"https://sdk.vercel.ai/docs/advanced/stopping-streams#ai-sdk-core\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">AI SDK</a>, forward the <code>abortSignal</code> to your stream:</p>\n   <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-code-block_wrapper__G_cQP\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:16px\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block_wrapper__t6FCO blog-code-block_codeBlock__s7CJU\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block_copyButton__uo5Yu code-block_copyFloatingButton__PsMvB\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-javascript code-block_pre___OLfy blog-code-block_maxHeight__pAjn3\"><code class=\"code-block_code__isn_V\"><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token imports punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token imports\"> openai </span><span class=\"token imports punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'@ai-sdk/openai'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token imports punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token imports\"> streamText </span><span class=\"token imports punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'ai'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword module\">export</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">async</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token constant\">POST</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">req</span><span class=\"token parameter operator\">:</span><span class=\"token parameter\"> Request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> prompt </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword control-flow\">await</span><span class=\"token plain\"> req</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">json</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> result </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">streamText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    model</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">openai</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'gpt-4-turbo'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    prompt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token comment\">// forward the abort signal:</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    abortSignal</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> req</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">signal</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token keyword control-flow\">return</span><span class=\"token plain\"> result</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">toTextStreamResponse</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:initial;--text-weight:400;--text-align:center\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Read more in the <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/functions/functions-api-reference#cancel-requests\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Functions documentation</a>.</p>\n  </div>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel 函数现已支持 Node.js 请求取消功能，从而优化资源利用。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel 函数现已支持 Node.js 请求取消功能，从而优化资源利用。",
  "summary": "Vercel 函数 (Node.js) 现在可以检测到请求取消，并在完成前停止执行。这包括离开页面、关闭选项卡或在 AI 聊天中点击停止以提前终止计算处理等操作。此功能通过监听 `Request.signal.aborted`（请求取消信号）或 `abort` 事件来实现，从而减少不必要的计算、令牌 (token) 生成以及避免发送用户不可见的数据。尤其是在 AI 应用中，通过传递 `abortSignal`（中止信号）可以有效停止流式数据生成，提升用户体验。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Vercel 函数现在支持请求取消功能。",
      "explanation": "允许开发者在客户端取消请求时，及时终止服务器端函数的执行，避免资源浪费。"
    },
    {
      "point": "可以通过 `Request.signal.aborted` 监听取消事件。",
      "explanation": "开发者可以通过监听请求取消信号 `Request.signal.aborted` 事件，在请求被取消时执行相应的清理操作，例如停止计算或关闭数据库连接。"
    },
    {
      "point": "请求取消功能增强了 Vercel 函数在处理异步任务时的灵活性和效率。",
      "explanation": "允许在 AI 应用中，当用户取消请求时，及时停止流式数据的生成，提高用户体验。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Vercel 函数使用 Node.js 现在可以检测到请求何时被取消，并在完成之前停止执行。",
    "这减少了不必要的计算、令牌 (token) 生成和发送用户看不到的数据。",
    "您可以使用 `Request.signal.aborted`（请求取消信号）或 [`abort`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbortSignal) 事件来监听取消。"
  ],
